msgctxt "sn23.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyamāravagga "
msgstr "2. About Māra (2nd) "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 14. Aniccadhammasutta → anicca 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn23.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Aniccadhammasutta "
msgstr "14. Naturally Impermanent "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.196, sc1
msgctxt "sn23.14:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.14:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.14:1.3"
msgid "“‘aniccadhammo, aniccadhammo’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘naturally impermanent’. "

msgctxt "sn23.14:1.4"
msgid "Katamo nu kho, bhante, aniccadhammo”ti? "
msgstr "What is naturally impermanent? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.14:1.5"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, aniccadhammo, vedanā aniccadhammo, saññā aniccadhammo, saṅkhārā aniccadhammo, viññāṇaṃ aniccadhammo. "
msgstr "“Rādha, form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness are naturally impermanent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.14:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn23.14:1.7"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.14:1.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
